HEADWORD: Bubonocele
<hw>Bu*bon"o*cele</hw> <pr>(b⟦usl⟧*b⟦ocr⟧n"⟦osl⟧*s⟦emac⟧l)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>boubw`n</grk> groin + <?/ tumor: cf. F.
